'''Robert Montgomerie''' (15 February 1880 &ndash; 28 April 1939) was a British Olympic [[fencing|fencer]]. He won two silver medals in the team [[<U+00E9>p<U+00E9>e]] competitions at the [[1908 Summer Olympics|1908]] and [[1912 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="databaseolympics">{{cite web |url=http://www.databaseolympics.com/players/playerpage.htm?ilkid=MONTGROB02 |title=Olympics Statistics: Robert Montgomerie |accessdate=2010-03-25 |work=databaseolympics.com}}</ref><ref name="sports-reference">{{cite web |url=http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/mo/robert-montgomerie-1.html |title=Robert Montgomerie Olympic Results |accessdate=2010-03-25 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>

